{"tid":568374,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"無懼 PIXEL 手機銷售慘淡，GOOGLE 對手機業務仍充滿信心！","createTime":"2018-02-21T17:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T12:55:49.000Z","uid":1886,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"5ad8238887397f0974ddaef76505f80cf00470e6","tid":568374,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T17:16:58.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/PIXEL_2_DXO_Mark_02-770x439_c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2FPIXEL_2_DXO_Mark_02-770x439_c.png&h=4953a9bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGoogle Pixel 手機推出已經有好一段時間，但因為銷售渠道不多，加上手機只有在歐美及印度地區推出。所以香港的消費者可能較難接觸到。到底在過去一年，Pixel 手機的銷量有多少呢? 日前，市場研究機構 IDC 日前就公佈了 Pixel 手機在 2017 年的整體銷售數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2018/02/16/%E7%84%A1%E6%87%BC-pixel-%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE%E6%85%98%E6%B7%A1-google-%E5%B0%8D%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%A5%AD%E5%8B%99%E4%BB%8D%E5%85%85%E6%BB%BF%E4%BF%A1%E5%BF%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2F2018%2F02%2F16%2F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2587%25BC-pixel-%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E9%258A%25B7%25E5%2594%25AE%25E6%2585%2598%25E6%25B7%25A1-google-%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%258B%2599%25E4%25BB%258D%25E5%2585%2585%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%25BF%2583%2F&d=GLZoUXEMF9Se%2F%2F9NfwqtiAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=d58df5b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2018/02/16/%E7%84%A1%E6%87%BC-pixel-%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE%E6%85%98%E6%B7%A1-google-%E5%B0%8D%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E6%A5%AD%E5%8B%99%E4%BB%8D%E5%85%85%E6%BB%BF%E4%BF%A1%E5%BF%83/</a></div>"},{"pid":"416384b091f19643e3b9f9f6c211ffb6211bf65b","tid":568374,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T17:17:41.000Z","msg":"根據 IDC 的報告指，Google 在 2017年共有 Pixel 和 Pixel 2 系列在內的 4 個機款發售，總出貨量為 390 萬部。但這個數字還比不上 iPhone 一星期的銷售數字。雖然 Pixel 手機銷售相當慘淡，但 Google 似乎對於手機業務的前景相當有信心，繼去年收購 台灣 htc Pixel 開發團隊之後，今年初亦有消息指 Pixel 2 系列手機會在台灣及其他華語地區發售，相信有助推動 Pixel 系列的銷售，亦有助 Google Assistant 中文化的發展。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/unnamed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2Funnamed.png&h=d9ecac60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Pixel 手機銷售相當慘淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></div>"},{"pid":"2e8bbc79aa22792fd21d2f31aa9820d2db87fee6","tid":568374,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":42,"score":-34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T17:20:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0681e60d2dcb77cb20c3459abd573e8614b7ab71","tid":568374,"uid":1886,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"quote":{"pid":"2e8bbc79aa22792fd21d2f31aa9820d2db87fee6","tid":568374,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":42,"score":-34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T17:20:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T17:22:09.000Z","msg":"無港行出乜撚新機都冇撚用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efee11f30da9df5b7b086843f8b4f024ac2376fb","tid":568374,"uid":1714,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T17:22:09.000Z","msg":"又po舊聞 中文傳媒真係好柒漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2728e90f6af2d6f8c1f665307e7428a959641fe","tid":568374,"uid":1714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efee11f30da9df5b7b086843f8b4f024ac2376fb","tid":568374,"uid":1714,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T17:22:09.000Z","msg":"又po舊聞 中文傳媒真係好柒漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyT